data.description: The Lakes, what a wonderful place to live. Many improvements on the way. This home has 4 and could be 5 or even 6 bedrooms if needed. 3 Bathroom. The home is has an open easy flow floorplan. Granite counter tops with tons of storage in the kitchen that overlooks the family room with fireplace. The 2nd floor has the huge master with double walk-in closets you just have to see this.3 other bedroom are on this level as well along with the laundry room. The 3rd floor is a large loft/office/platroom or bedroom. 3 car garage with a lot of storage.Great curb appeal on this home.   The home is being worked on and improved but is still very easy to show. Please call or text  for appointment.      The community has a Private pool, spa,BBQ area, walking trails, playground and so much more all inside this gated neighborhood.
